<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继母嘲笑灰姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你？”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不可能是你的鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你没有去参加舞会。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信使看了看灰姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她穿着破衣，但是......</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子给信使下了命令。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个姑娘都必须试穿这只鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘深吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她慢慢地把脚伸进水晶鞋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的继姐姐们大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鞋子合适？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信使眨了眨眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是你！”他大喊道，“你就是公主！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继母跺着脚走向灰姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可能！”她厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你从没离开过这座房子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘把手伸进口袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿出另一只鞋穿上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，仙女出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女挥舞她的魔杖。噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘又成了美丽的公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格特和特鲁迪各行了个屈膝礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们非常抱歉。”她们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继母抱着她的胳膊。“哼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信使笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请跟我来！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子会很高兴的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，灰姑娘回到了宫殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三天后， 她和王子举行了婚礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘现在真的是公主了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她还是很善良。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，灰姑娘邀请她的继姐姐们和她住在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她甚至邀请了继母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从此以后，他们都过上了幸福的生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>